---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Hakkımızda | Şanlıurfa Klima Servisi"
  description="Şanlıurfa Klima Servisi hakkında - Ekibimizi, hikayemizi ve değerlerimizi tanıyın. Sertifikalı teknisyenler, güvenilir hizmet."
  activePage="about"
>
  <!-- ============ SECTION 1: HERO ============ -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-brand-navy" style="min-height: 320px;">
    <!-- Background image with overlay -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src="/brand_assets/technician-rooftop.webp" alt="Ekibimiz" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center">
      <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(26,46,59,0.92) 50%, rgba(26,46,59,0.65) 100%);"></div>
    </div>
    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-col justify-center" style="min-height: 320px;">
      <div class="py-16">
        <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-400 text-sm mb-5">
          <a href="/" class="footer-link hover:text-brand-orange">Ana Sayfa</a>
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          <span class="text-gray-300">Hakkımızda</span>
        </nav>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-[-0.03em] leading-[1.1]">EKİBİMİZLE TANISIN</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Wave bottom -->
    <svg class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full" viewBox="0 0 1440 72" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <path d="M0,72 C480,10 960,10 1440,72 L1440,72 L0,72 Z" fill="white"/>
    </svg>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ SECTION 2: HOW IT ALL STARTED ============ -->
  <section class="bg-white pt-20 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <!-- Photo -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-card mb-10 relative">
        <img src="/brand_assets/technician-customer-indoor.webp" alt="Klima servis ekibi" class="w-full h-72 sm:h-96 object-cover">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/40 to-transparent"></div>
      </div>
      <!-- Heading -->
      <span class="text-brand-orange font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Hikayemiz</span>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-navy mt-3 mb-6 tracking-[-0.03em]">NASIL BAŞLADIK?</h2>
      <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-brand-orange mx-auto mb-8 rounded-full"></div>
      <p class="text-text-body text-base mb-5" style="line-height: 1.8;">
        Şanlıurfa Klima Servisi, şehrin sıcak yazları ve soğuk kışlarında vatandaşların konforunu sağlamak amacıyla kuruldu. Kurucumuz, sektörde başka firmalarda çalışırken müşteri memnuniyetinin yeterince ön planda tutulmadığını fark etti. Farklı bir şey yaratma vakti gelmişti — dürüst fiyatlar, zamanında hizmet ve gerçek kalite.
      </p>
      <p class="text-text-body text-base" style="line-height: 1.8;">
        O günden bu yana Şanlıurfa Klima Servisi, Haliliye'den Karaköprü'ye, Eyyübiye'den şehir merkezine kadar binlerce haneye ve işyerine hizmet vermiş, güvenilir servis anlayışını bölgenin referans noktası haline getirmiştir. Ekibimiz her işte en yüksek standardı korur; müşteri memnuniyetimiz her zaman önceliğimizdir.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ SECTION 3: TRUST BADGES ============ -->
  <section class="bg-white py-10 border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-8 sm:gap-14">
        <!-- Google -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1.5">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-body uppercase tracking-wide">Google 5 Yıldız</span>
        </div>
        <!-- Divider -->
        <div class="hidden sm:block w-px h-12 bg-gray-200"></div>
        <!-- Lisanslı & Sigortalı -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1.5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-body uppercase tracking-wide">Lisanslı &amp; Sigortalı</span>
        </div>
        <!-- Divider -->
        <div class="hidden sm:block w-px h-12 bg-gray-200"></div>
        <!-- 7/24 Servis -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1.5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-orange/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-body uppercase tracking-wide">7/24 Acil Servis</span>
        </div>
        <!-- Divider -->
        <div class="hidden sm:block w-px h-12 bg-gray-200"></div>
        <!-- Facebook -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1.5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-body uppercase tracking-wide">Facebook Onaylı</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ SECTION 4: BAKIM PROGRAMI BANNER ============ -->
  <section class="relative bg-brand-teal py-20 overflow-hidden mt-10">
    <!-- Wave top -->
    <svg class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full" viewBox="0 0 1440 60" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="margin-top:-1px;">
      <path d="M0,0 L1440,0 L1440,60 C960,5 480,5 0,60 Z" fill="white"/>
    </svg>
    <!-- Background texture -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
      <img src="/brand_assets/background-bokeh.webp" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <span class="inline-block text-white/70 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Özel Fırsat</span>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-[2.6rem] font-extrabold text-white tracking-[-0.03em] mb-5">BAKIM PROGRAMIMIZA KATILIM!</h2>
      <p class="text-white/80 text-base max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-9" style="line-height: 1.7;">
        Klimanızı her zaman verimli tutmak için yıllık bakım programımıza dahil olun. Düzenli kontrol, filtre temizliği ve gaz seviyesi takibi ile arıza maliyetlerini sıfırın. Uzun vadeli konfor garantisi sizin için.
      </p>
      <a href="/#contact" class="btn-orange inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-brand-orange text-white font-bold text-base px-9 py-4 rounded-full focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-white focus-visible:outline-offset-2">
        Daha Fazla Bilgi
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
    <!-- Wave bottom -->
    <svg class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full" viewBox="0 0 1440 60" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <path d="M0,60 C480,5 960,5 1440,60 L1440,60 L0,60 Z" fill="#f5f0eb"/>
    </svg>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ SECTION 5: KLAS CORE VALUES ============ -->
  <section class="relative bg-brand-cream pt-20 pb-24 overflow-hidden">
    <!-- SVG wavy texture -->
    <svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full opacity-[0.04]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <filter id="noise"><feTurbulence type="fractalNoise" baseFrequency="0.65" numOctaves="3" stitchTiles="stitch"/><feColorMatrix type="saturate" values="0"/></filter>
      <rect width="100%" height="100%" filter="url(#noise)"/>
    </svg>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Label -->
      <div class="text-center mb-6">
        <span class="text-brand-teal font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Temel Değerlerimiz</span>
      </div>

      <!-- KLAS letters -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:gap-8 mb-16">
        <span class="klas-letter">K</span>
        <span class="klas-letter">L</span>
        <span class="klas-letter">A</span>
        <span class="klas-letter">S</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Three-column layout: portrait | center value | portrait -->
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-10 lg:gap-8">

        <!-- Left portrait -->
        <div class="w-52 h-52 sm:w-64 sm:h-64 rounded-full overflow-hidden shadow-card flex-shrink-0 relative">
          <img src="/brand_assets/testimonial-ahmet.webp" alt="Ekip üyesi" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full" style="background: radial-gradient(circle at center, transparent 60%, rgba(42,125,138,0.15) 100%);"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Center: value description -->
        <div class="flex-1 text-center max-w-md mx-auto">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-2xl text-brand-navy mb-4 tracking-tight">Kültür</h3>
          <p class="text-text-body text-base" style="line-height: 1.8;">
            Şanlıurfa Klima Servisi olarak iş birliği ve mükemmel hizmet sunmayı kendimize şiar edindik. Ekibimizin ortak ruhu, şirketi değil; bir topluluk kurmayı hedefler. Her işte kalite, liderlik, aile bağı ve gerçek servis anlayışıyla hareket ediyoruz.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Right portrait -->
        <div class="w-52 h-52 sm:w-64 sm:h-64 rounded-full overflow-hidden shadow-card flex-shrink-0 relative">
          <img src="/brand_assets/testimonial-fatma.webp" alt="Ekip üyesi" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full" style="background: radial-gradient(circle at center, transparent 60%, rgba(232,100,44,0.12) 100%);"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Value pills row -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mt-14">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-card px-6 py-4 flex items-center gap-3 min-w-[140px]">
          <span class="text-brand-teal font-extrabold text-2xl font-heading">K</span>
          <div>
            <div class="font-heading font-bold text-brand-navy text-sm">Kalite</div>
            <div class="text-text-body text-xs">Her işte mükemmellik</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-card px-6 py-4 flex items-center gap-3 min-w-[140px]">
          <span class="text-brand-teal font-extrabold text-2xl font-heading">L</span>
          <div>
            <div class="font-heading font-bold text-brand-navy text-sm">Liderlik</div>
            <div class="text-text-body text-xs">Sektörde öncü olmak</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-card px-6 py-4 flex items-center gap-3 min-w-[140px]">
          <span class="text-brand-teal font-extrabold text-2xl font-heading">A</span>
          <div>
            <div class="font-heading font-bold text-brand-navy text-sm">Aile</div>
            <div class="text-text-body text-xs">Müşteri odaklı ilişki</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-card px-6 py-4 flex items-center gap-3 min-w-[140px]">
          <span class="text-brand-teal font-extrabold text-2xl font-heading">S</span>
          <div>
            <div class="font-heading font-bold text-brand-navy text-sm">Servis</div>
            <div class="text-text-body text-xs">7/24 güvenilir destek</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ SECTION 6: SERVICE AREA ============ -->
  <section class="bg-white py-0">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row" style="min-height: 420px;">
      <!-- Left: Map -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 relative overflow-hidden" style="min-height: 320px;">
        <iframe
          src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d200000!2d38.7969!3d37.1591!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x153477a5a5e7e5c7%3A0x1234!2s%C5%9Eanl%C4%B1urfa!5e0!3m2!1str!2str!4v1"
          width="100%" height="100%" style="border:0; min-height: 420px;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
        </iframe>
      </div>
      <!-- Right: Dark panel -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 bg-brand-navy flex items-center" style="min-height: 420px;">
        <div class="px-10 py-14 lg:px-16 max-w-lg">
          <span class="text-brand-orange font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Hizmet Bölgelerimiz</span>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mt-3 mb-5 tracking-[-0.03em]">EN İYİ HİZMETİ NEREDE VERİYORUZ?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-base mb-8" style="line-height: 1.7;">
            Şanlıurfa'nın tüm ilçelerini kapsayan hizmet ağımızla yanınızdayız. Haliliye, Karaköprü ve Eyyübiye başta olmak üzere Viranşehir, Birecik ve Suruç dahil geniş bir coğrafyada kaliteli klima hizmeti sunuyoruz.
          </p>
          <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-8">
            <li class="bg-white/10 text-white text-sm px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Haliliye</li>
            <li class="bg-white/10 text-white text-sm px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Karaköprü</li>
            <li class="bg-white/10 text-white text-sm px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Eyyübiye</li>
            <li class="bg-white/10 text-white text-sm px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Viranşehir</li>
            <li class="bg-white/10 text-white text-sm px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Birecik</li>
            <li class="bg-white/10 text-white text-sm px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Suruç</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/#contact" class="btn-orange inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-brand-orange text-white font-bold text-sm px-7 py-3.5 rounded-full focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-brand-orange focus-visible:outline-offset-2">
            Bize Ulaşın
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ SECTION 7: COMMUNITY TRUST ============ -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12 lg:gap-16">
        <!-- Left: Text -->
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
          <span class="text-brand-orange font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Topluma Katkımız</span>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-navy mt-3 mb-6 tracking-[-0.03em]">TOPLUMA DEĞER KATIYORUZ</h2>
          <p class="text-text-body text-base mb-6" style="line-height: 1.8;">
            Kaliteli hizmet sunmanın ötesine geçerek Şanlıurfa'ya değer katmanın yollarını arıyoruz. Yerel esnaf dernekleriyle iş birliği yapıyor, Haliliye ve Eyyübiye'de sosyal sorumluluk projelerine destek veriyoruz. Küçük bir şehir firması olarak büyüme hedefimiz; önce insana, sonra işe.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-body text-base mb-9" style="line-height: 1.8;">
            Ekibimiz Şanlıurfa'nın birer çocuğu — bu topraklarda yaşıyor, burada büyüyor. Müşterilerimizi komşumuz gibi görüyor; ev sahiplerine, işletmelere ve okullara en dürüst hizmeti sunmaya özen gösteriyoruz.
          </p>
          <a href="/#contact" class="btn-orange inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-brand-orange text-white font-bold text-sm px-7 py-3.5 rounded-full focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-brand-orange focus-visible:outline-offset-2">
            Bize Ulaşın
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <!-- Right: Photo -->
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 relative">
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-card relative">
            <img src="/brand_assets/technician-outdoor.webp" alt="Topluma katkı" class="w-full h-80 sm:h-96 object-cover">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/40 to-transparent"></div>
          </div>
          <!-- Accent decoration -->
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 w-20 h-20 bg-brand-orange/20 rounded-2xl -z-10"></div>
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-16 h-16 bg-brand-teal/15 rounded-full -z-10"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ SECTION 8: NEWSLETTER / TIPS ============ -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-brand-cream rounded-2xl shadow-card p-8 sm:p-12 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Noise texture -->
        <svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full opacity-[0.03]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <filter id="tipNoise"><feTurbulence type="fractalNoise" baseFrequency="0.65" numOctaves="3" stitchTiles="stitch"/><feColorMatrix type="saturate" values="0"/></filter>
          <rect width="100%" height="100%" filter="url(#tipNoise)"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <span class="text-brand-orange font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Bülten</span>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand-navy mt-3 mb-4 tracking-[-0.03em]">FAYDALI İPUÇLARI VE GÜNCELLEMELER ALIN</h2>
          <p class="text-text-body text-base mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto" style="line-height: 1.7;">Klima bakımı, enerji tasarrufu ve sezonluk öneriler hakkında düzenli bilgilendirmeler doğrudan e-postanıza gelsin.</p>
          <form class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-3 max-w-md mx-auto" onsubmit="event.preventDefault();">
            <input type="email" placeholder="E-posta adresiniz" class="w-full sm:flex-1 px-5 py-3.5 rounded-full border border-gray-200 text-sm text-brand-navy placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-orange/40 focus:border-brand-orange bg-white">
